     At a time when foreign <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC:CORPORATION">banks</ENAMEX> are pouring vast resources and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">personnel</ENAMEX> into <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE:COUNTRY">West Germany</ENAMEX> 's financial <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC:CITY">center</ENAMEX> , the opening of a <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">three</NUMEX>-man <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC:CORPORATION">office</ENAMEX> on a <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE:CITY">Frankfurt</ENAMEX> side <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC:HIGHWAY_STREET">street</ENAMEX> should n't attract much attention .
