     <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Paul Lesutis</ENAMEX> , who manages <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">more than $ 3 billion</NUMEX> of investments at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION:CORPORATION">Provident Capital Management Inc.</ENAMEX> , blames futures markets for leading the way .
